item.title: CVE-2010-2476|2024-08-07T02:32:16.836Z -- syscp -- syscp
item.description: syscp 1.4.2.1 allows attackers to add arbitrary paths via the documentroot of a domain by appending a colon to it and setting the open basedir path to use that domain documentroot.
